{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I have a big impact on the planet"},{"time":4000,"text":"to travel here by plane."},{"time":7000,"text":"I emitted, in the atmosphere, nine tons of CO2;"},{"time":14000,"text":"that is the weight of two elephants."},{"time":17000,"text":"I came here to speak about ecology,"},{"time":20000,"text":"and I emitted as much CO2"},{"time":23000,"text":"as a Frenchman in one year."},{"time":26000,"text":"So what do I have to do?"},{"time":28000,"text":"I have to kill a Frenchman when I come back at home?"},{"time":30000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":32000,"text":"I have to do my carbon offset in another way,"},{"time":35000,"text":"like I do every time."},{"time":37000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":40000,"text":"In fact my work is to show"},{"time":45000,"text":"our impact on our planet."},{"time":49000,"text":"I'm going to show you some examples"},{"time":51000,"text":"of the last pictures I've done"},{"time":53000,"text":"in the last year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":57000,"text":"Alberta sand oil, a lot of pollution."},{"time":62000,"text":"You know the problem;"},{"time":64000,"text":"we don't want to believe what we know."},{"time":70000,"text":"In Alberta people work nonstop,"},{"time":73000,"text":"24 hours by seven"},{"time":76000,"text":"to extract as much oil"},{"time":78000,"text":"as they can."},{"time":80000,"text":"We know about the end of oil."},{"time":83000,"text":"Oil sand is not a long-term solution."},{"time":87000,"text":"But we use three times more oil"},{"time":91000,"text":"than we find every year."},{"time":93000,"text":"We don't want to believe what we know."},{"time":95000,"text":"Deny."}]},{"cues":[{"time":97000,"text":"Coral reef in New Caledonia."},{"time":101000,"text":"100 percent of the coral"},{"time":104000,"text":"may be wiped out before 2050"},{"time":107000,"text":"because of global warming."},{"time":109000,"text":"And you know how coral are very sensitive to temperature,"},{"time":113000,"text":"and are very important for the biodiversity of the sea."}]},{"cues":[{"time":119000,"text":"North Pole. I've done this picture last summer."},{"time":123000,"text":"It was impossible to do this picture 15 years ago."},{"time":127000,"text":"Now there is a new way open between Atlantic and Pacific."},{"time":133000,"text":"The thickness of the Arctic"},{"time":137000,"text":"decreased more than 40 percent"},{"time":140000,"text":"since 1960."}]},{"cues":[{"time":145000,"text":"There is a new face of Kilimanjaro without ice."},{"time":149000,"text":"Sad picture."},{"time":151000,"text":"It lost 80 percent of its ice."},{"time":154000,"text":"According to scientists,"},{"time":156000,"text":"in 100 years"},{"time":159000,"text":"all the mountain glacier will be gone."},{"time":162000,"text":"Glaciers are very important for the life on earth."},{"time":166000,"text":"Like Al Gore told you,"},{"time":168000,"text":"two billion people live on the water"},{"time":170000,"text":"from the glacier of Himalaya."}]},{"cues":[{"time":173000,"text":"Return of fish men."},{"time":175000,"text":"One fifth of human kind"},{"time":180000,"text":"depend on fish to live."},{"time":183000,"text":"Today now 70 percent"},{"time":187000,"text":"of the fish stock are over-exploited."},{"time":190000,"text":"According to FAO,"},{"time":194000,"text":"if we don't change our system of fishing"},{"time":197000,"text":"the main sea resources will be gone in 2050."},{"time":201000,"text":"We don't want to believe what we know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":205000,"text":"The beautiful picture, by [unclear] in Africa."},{"time":210000,"text":"One human of six"},{"time":212000,"text":"have not enough to eat in the world."},{"time":215000,"text":"One billion people have not enough to eat."},{"time":218000,"text":"In Africa, corn is one of the main foods in many places."},{"time":224000,"text":"Here in America,"},{"time":226000,"text":"90 percent of the corn cultivated"},{"time":230000,"text":"is used to feed animals or to do oil."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235000,"text":"Palm tree plantation in Borneo."},{"time":239000,"text":"Every year we lose 50 thousand square miles in deforestation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249000,"text":"Refugee camp in Darfur."},{"time":252000,"text":"Today we have 20 million refugees in the world."},{"time":256000,"text":"According to the U.N.,"},{"time":258000,"text":"we speak about 250 million refugees"},{"time":261000,"text":"in 2050."}]},{"cues":[{"time":267000,"text":"I always show my pictures in the street."},{"time":270000,"text":"We have done already 100 exhibitions in the cities."},{"time":273000,"text":"But how to understand the world"},{"time":277000,"text":"without the voice of people?"},{"time":280000,"text":"Landscape was not enough."},{"time":283000,"text":"It was obvious to me to do another work."},{"time":286000,"text":"I launched a project named Six Billion Others."},{"time":291000,"text":"I sent around the world six cameramen"},{"time":294000,"text":"asking the same question,"},{"time":297000,"text":"the same crucial question,"},{"time":299000,"text":"about life."},{"time":301000,"text":"We have done five thousand interviews."},{"time":304000,"text":"I'm going to show you this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":312000,"text":"Man: The most beautiful thing that has happened to me in life?"},{"time":315000,"text":"It's when my dad told me, \"Here, I give you this girl as your fiance.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":322000,"text":"Woman: Love? Love is nice if you can have it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":326000,"text":"Second Man: Romeo and Juliet, Sassi and Panno, Dodi and Diana, Heer and Ranjha,"},{"time":329000,"text":"this is love! Third Man: My greatest fear is ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332000,"text":"Woman: You're asking me a hard question."}]},{"cues":[{"time":334000,"text":"Fourth Man: I live happily because what else should I do?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":337000,"text":"Fifth Man: The first thing I remember ... (Sixth Man: That's how I learned, by my mother,)"},{"time":341000,"text":"Fifth Man: ... from my childhood, (Sixth Man: that you should respect humans.)"},{"time":344000,"text":"Fifth Man: we were having fun, biking. (Sixth Man: I will never forget those words.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":347000,"text":"Seventh Man: We invented stories, we flew around the world, while remaining in our attic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353000,"text":"Eighth Man: I had a big laugh today."},{"time":355000,"text":"Ninth Man: You see, family is ... it's awful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360000,"text":"10th Man: In the word life, you have the life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362000,"text":"11th Man: Who am I? Isn't that the biggest question?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":368000,"text":"12th Man: If I was to go back to Iraq"},{"time":370000,"text":"and speak to the people,"},{"time":372000,"text":"I'd have to bow down and kiss their feet."},{"time":374000,"text":"Just as that woman tried to kiss my feet"},{"time":377000,"text":"when we were taking her sons."},{"time":381000,"text":"I feel ashamed."},{"time":384000,"text":"And I feel humbled"},{"time":386000,"text":"by their strength."},{"time":388000,"text":"And I will forever feel a need"},{"time":391000,"text":"to make reparations to Iraq."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398000,"text":"Second Woman: Dad, Mom, I grew up."},{"time":402000,"text":"You shouldn't worry about me. Dad doesn't need to go to work."},{"time":407000,"text":"My family ... What can I say?"},{"time":411000,"text":"At the moment, my family is very poor,"},{"time":414000,"text":"my life here in Shenzhen is just about showing myself that I can earn more"},{"time":422000,"text":"and to let my parents stay and have something to live on."},{"time":426000,"text":"I don't want them to spend their whole lives in poverty."},{"time":432000,"text":"If someday I can achieve something, I would like to say thank you daddy and mommy."},{"time":442000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":445000,"text":"Thank you for having fed me and raised me,"},{"time":448000,"text":"and for making my life of today. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":454000,"text":"13th Man: After seven years now of being in a wheelchair,"},{"time":457000,"text":"I've done more in life being in a chair"},{"time":460000,"text":"than out of a chair."},{"time":462000,"text":"I still surf. I sail the world. I freedive."},{"time":466000,"text":"After many people said I couldn't do that."},{"time":471000,"text":"And I think that comes from connecting with nature,"},{"time":474000,"text":"connecting with the energy of life,"},{"time":477000,"text":"because we're all disabled in some way on the planet --"},{"time":479000,"text":"spiritually, mentally or physically."},{"time":483000,"text":"I got the easy part."}]},{"cues":[{"time":488000,"text":"14th Man: Let's say that you and me like each other."},{"time":492000,"text":"You come from elsewhere."},{"time":494000,"text":"You don't know me. I don't know you."},{"time":499000,"text":"We talk without lying."},{"time":501000,"text":"If I do like you, I give you one cow and many other things"},{"time":506000,"text":"and we become friends."},{"time":509000,"text":"How can we make it all by ourselves?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":530000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":538000,"text":"YAB: You can also go to the website,"},{"time":540000,"text":"answer -- respond to the questions also."},{"time":543000,"text":"Forty crucial questions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":545000,"text":"Now I am going to speak to you about my movie."},{"time":548000,"text":"For the last three years,"},{"time":550000,"text":"I was shooting the earth for the movie."},{"time":554000,"text":"The name of the movie is \"Home\" --"},{"time":557000,"text":"\"Maison.\""},{"time":560000,"text":"It is about the state of the planet."},{"time":563000,"text":"It's a fantastic story of life on the earth."},{"time":567000,"text":"I'm very proud to show you the teaser."}]},{"cues":[{"time":570000,"text":"Video: This Earth is four and a half billion years old."},{"time":583000,"text":"These plants, several hundred million years old."},{"time":588000,"text":"And we humans have been walking upright"},{"time":591000,"text":"for only 200 thousand years."},{"time":596000,"text":"We've managed to adapt,"},{"time":597000,"text":"and have conquered the whole planet."},{"time":603000,"text":"For generations, we've been raising our children,"},{"time":606000,"text":"not unlike millions of other species living beside us."},{"time":612000,"text":"For the past 30 years"},{"time":614000,"text":"I've been closely watching the earth and its dwellers"},{"time":617000,"text":"from high up in the sky."},{"time":619000,"text":"Our life is tied to the well-being of our planet."},{"time":624000,"text":"We depend on water,"},{"time":627000,"text":"forests,"},{"time":629000,"text":"deserts,"},{"time":632000,"text":"oceans."},{"time":635000,"text":"Fishing,"},{"time":637000,"text":"breeding,"},{"time":639000,"text":"farming"},{"time":641000,"text":"are still the world's foremost human occupations."},{"time":646000,"text":"And what binds us together"},{"time":648000,"text":"is far greater than what divides us."},{"time":652000,"text":"We all share the same need for the earth's gifts --"},{"time":657000,"text":"the same wish to rise above ourselves,"},{"time":659000,"text":"and become better."},{"time":664000,"text":"And yet we carry on raising walls"},{"time":666000,"text":"to keep us apart."}]},{"cues":[{"time":669000,"text":"Today our greatest battle"},{"time":671000,"text":"is to protect the natural offerings of our planet."},{"time":674000,"text":"In less than 50 years"},{"time":676000,"text":"we've altered it more thoroughly"},{"time":678000,"text":"than in the entire history of mankind."},{"time":681000,"text":"Half of the world's forests have vanished."},{"time":684000,"text":"Water resources are running low."},{"time":686000,"text":"Intensive farming is depleting soils."},{"time":691000,"text":"Our energy sources are not sustainable."},{"time":694000,"text":"The climate is changing."},{"time":696000,"text":"We are endangering ourselves."},{"time":699000,"text":"We're only trying to improve our lives."},{"time":702000,"text":"But the wealth gaps are growing wider."},{"time":705000,"text":"We haven't yet understood"},{"time":707000,"text":"that we're going at a much faster pace"},{"time":710000,"text":"than the planet can sustain."},{"time":732000,"text":"We know that solutions are available today."},{"time":738000,"text":"We all have the power to change this trend"},{"time":741000,"text":"for the better."},{"time":748000,"text":"So what are we waiting for?"},{"time":773000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":781000,"text":"YAB: Luc Besson is the producer of the movie."},{"time":785000,"text":"But it is not a normal movie."},{"time":789000,"text":"The film is going to be distributed free."},{"time":794000,"text":"This film has no copyright."},{"time":798000,"text":"On the five of June,"},{"time":801000,"text":"the environment day,"},{"time":804000,"text":"everybody can download the movie on Internet."},{"time":808000,"text":"The film is given for free"},{"time":812000,"text":"to the distributor for TV and theater"},{"time":816000,"text":"to show it the fifth of June."},{"time":819000,"text":"There is no business on this movie."},{"time":822000,"text":"It is also available for school,"},{"time":824000,"text":"cities, NGOs and you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":829000,"text":"We have to believe what we know."},{"time":833000,"text":"Let me tell you something."},{"time":837000,"text":"It's too late to be pessimistic --"},{"time":840000,"text":"really too late."},{"time":844000,"text":"We have all a part of the solutions."},{"time":851000,"text":"To finish,"},{"time":853000,"text":"I would like to welcome"},{"time":857000,"text":"the 4,700th baby"},{"time":860000,"text":"born since the beginning of this talk."},{"time":866000,"text":"Merci beaucoup. I love you."},{"time":868000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}